title: Box And Cover, 1853–70
creditline: Gift of Mary M. Kenway from the estate of Sarah B. Russell
description: Rectangular box covered with watered white paper. (B) Cover, with watered paper on outside, edges framed with gold paper.  Oval label on top "550 Broadway 552 + Tiffany Compy + New York." Inside, large label printed in lavender.

tombstone.epitaph:
Box And Cover, 1853–70.
1853–70. Cardboard. Gift of Mary M. Kenway from the estate of Sarah B. Russell. 1956-32-78-a,b.
